{"tid":57104,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(足球新手)點解我點踢都咁廢","createTime":"2016-12-27T18:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T22:20:48.000Z","uid":63979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4216f2497a114208d022f47c6b1470f91fd0c16","tid":57104,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:02:59.000Z","msg":"廢到成日比隊友屌，<br />\n控波又唔多掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n我反應又慢，往往個波黎到我先有反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都好鍾意踢波，各位巴打有無解決辦法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de365951553ba16af90b1b52d6029fb1e3f1f90","tid":57104,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:04:21.000Z","msg":"用手踢試下"},{"pid":"d5caa93f2c9d29b7185602ea3901ea189434819d","tid":57104,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:07:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢到成日比隊友屌，<br />\n控波又唔多掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n我反應又慢，往往個波黎到我先有反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都好鍾意踢波，各位巴打有無解決辦法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵個好波啲嘅同你玩one touch互傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd777a6aeaabf7dd196edc085ef212ce96b689d","tid":57104,"uid":75,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:13:31.000Z","msg":"唔好怕麻煩怕悶<br />\n自己買個波落波地練吓帶波擺啲雜物喺地下<br />\n練吓S形盤球又好，掉頭又好<br />\n總之慢慢帶個波，熟咗就加快速度<br />\n如果有朋友一齊練就梗係最好，齋練掃把腳傳波都已經好好多<br />\n冇波都唔緊要，如果體能好的話幫手追波，攔截都有用<br />\n得閒跑吓步啦"},{"pid":"dd6305ca49318bb7ca049e63f840d20d95469b38","tid":57104,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:06:37.000Z","msg":"技術差嘅話一定係用體能、鳩跑、鳩撞去搭救"},{"pid":"2c7ff6988855dc6add549cf58a8288c0e6a97111","tid":57104,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:13:32.000Z","msg":"試下打龍"},{"pid":"4c220611e652d154a831ff1aecd9090aea828c96","tid":57104,"uid":8167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:17:17.000Z","msg":"踢後囉 <br />\n有波俾左右 <br />\n有信心就俾中場 <br />\n防守mark 緊啲 唔好亂出腳 <br />\n跟住就ok 斬波埋黎 你就用多啲手 擴開自己個位"},{"pid":"a97ef0388be7f8f1f88eb8e2217d2076ea2d3cd8","tid":57104,"uid":8167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:18:15.000Z","msg":"太近龍 唔好放佢射"},{"pid":"2eacad25a05b1e2ce61d73af12e6af5cf83d25de","tid":57104,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:19:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>技術差嘅話一定係用體能、鳩跑、鳩撞去搭救</blockquote><br />\n岩, 自知技術麻麻但跑都唔跑果D真係不如唔好落場<br />\n有D同D唔係好識踢GE踢如果肯跑下都冇乜野<br />\n但見過好多真係企係度養生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔諗下應該做D咩, 又唔追下人, 對住呢D真係好撚燥<br />\n成日睇波睇波都唔知睇左D咩出黎"},{"pid":"752c6e002e2d8325da4f52e642d50d64bfa2f04e","tid":57104,"uid":8167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:21:15.000Z","msg":"最緊要係肯跑 <br />\n我有fd 都無新手 矮的<br />\n肯跑 肯追波，mark 緊啲人 就算佢唔太識hold 波都少俾人屌 <br />\n有波就傳左先  有空位先自己帶 <br />\n傳波 走位 回防 跑多啲 腳下功夫唔洗好 <br />\n傳波準就ok"},{"pid":"cbe7ea2fb2ffb6de86b53f29d602e0bfd00b1b35","tid":57104,"uid":4155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:33:22.000Z","msg":"百屌成材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0ac496b0ac2d39627069bf79faea764f4c0cd1","tid":57104,"uid":43015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ3c2d3Qa9cs8t7Qyx1cgko3mFw7WmQkJQ1KY6M5YGjUa?filename=77fSx6s.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F77fSx6s.gif&h=3424a819&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2af056c0e588300409074455ac7f39b5f91987dc","tid":57104,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:51:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢到成日比隊友屌，<br />\n控波又唔多掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n我反應又慢，往往個波黎到我先有反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都好鍾意踢波，各位巴打有無解決辦法呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n參加啲足球訓練班由頭學起"},{"pid":"75d5e83edb0f315488400e2689a3c0fd9146967c","tid":57104,"uid":847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T19:57:34.000Z","msg":"又廢又唔撚郁真係唔好落場 <br />\n同打少個無分別<br />\n<br />\n係鐘意踢波既就自動自覺練好基本功"},{"pid":"a27d3dd10a0a291271bd99fc02c153155f8bd360","tid":57104,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又廢又唔撚郁真係唔好落場 <br />\n同打少個無分別<br />\n<br />\n係鐘意踢波既就自動自覺練好基本功</blockquote><br />\n後半句totally agger"},{"pid":"34f5db90c5cd553ae215bfb495a4354db80c042f","tid":57104,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:02:01.000Z","msg":"認真，練好基本功先"},{"pid":"b028ab2415f91daab4b98b3737b07cca475f924f","tid":57104,"uid":6068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:04:20.000Z","msg":"其實好簡單<br />\n練基本功啦<br />\n練好傳控地波<br />\n再到斬控高波<br />\n之後扭波射波<br />\n一步一步黎<br />\n同埋儘量令自己唔好依賴 身體質素 同 速度<br />\n有咩問pm啦"},{"pid":"da787eda2058c3e889000c28102014d298f29000","tid":57104,"uid":55830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:04:28.000Z","msg":"我都踢左好耐 要我控高波真係好差....成日控唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申踢左好多年龍 間中都會出下黎打閘"},{"pid":"e015eebe6453e9831bee03115d89f28d923aab34","tid":57104,"uid":37168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:05:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都踢左好耐 要我控高波真係好差....成日控唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申踢左好多年龍 間中都會出下黎打閘</blockquote><br />\n踢高粒波俾自己控返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3605065cf7837a93da95665ab92dc067edb827e","tid":57104,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:06:46.000Z","msg":"最基本既係睇下識踼既人教踼波<br />\n呢個kk足球教室真心實用<br />\n幾年前睇完再練，基本功進步好多<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.youku.com/video/id_XNjU1NzY1NjE2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.youku.com%2Fvideo%2Fid_XNjU1NzY1NjE2.html&d=%2BtbibQSoubMVXvrlaH3wyQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=f2efa2b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.youku.com/video/id_XNjU1NzY1NjE2.html</a>"},{"pid":"5a5baa02eded1b9812d30388bdacceb4fecd4333","tid":57104,"uid":3595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:11:26.000Z","msg":"睇多啲波都好有用<br />\n但唔好真係淨睇<br />\n要留意下啲球員既動作<br />\n<br />\n無咩技術就盡量踢得簡單啲<br />\n踢一腳波 有波埋黎控定就盡快交波俾隊友<br />\n<br />\n同埋盡量唔好成日淨係望住地下個波<br />\n多啲留意隊友既位置咁就可以俾自己多啲時間去處理個波"},{"pid":"a930bbbc0e9569e2c8d7a380af58414b8d5e25e9","tid":57104,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:14:46.000Z","msg":"練的波，熟習個球感先"},{"pid":"a5a65d867f5ce5c99ca75160a20a3654cb635375","tid":57104,"uid":16031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:17:19.000Z","msg":"睇多d我踢波"},{"pid":"81ce621936160318fb939ec6528b9ce991850ea7","tid":57104,"uid":65198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T22:20:48.000Z","msg":"自己踢多D 唔得既跑多幾步 幫手mark 下人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}